Package: outbreakteachR
Type: Package
Title: Demonstration of analysis associated to "paper outbreak" teaching practical
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Oliver Waton
Maintainer: Oliver Watson <o.watson@imperial.ac.uk>
Description: Importing and analysing data sheet created within teaching "paper
    outbreak". Tools include visualisation and animation of the outbreak dynamics,
    example simualtion methods.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0),
    ndtv
Imports:
    network (>= 1.13),
    networkDynamic (>= 0.9),
    animation (>= 2.4),
    sna,
    ggplot2,
    scales (>= 0.4.1),
    igraph,
    reshape2,
    readxl,
    extrafont,
    statnet.common,
    base64,
    plyr,
    rlang
